exists": "", "*": "Template:Seq/styles.css"}, {"ns": 10, "exists": "", "*": "Template:Rulingstewards"}, {"ns": 10, "exists": "", "*": "Template:Southernline"}, {"ns": 10, "exists": "", "*": "Template:SA"}, {"ns": 10, "exists": "", "*": "Template:FoA"}, {"ns": 10, "exists": "", "*": "Template:Title"}, {"ns": 828, "exists": "", "*": "Module:Paramvalidate"}, {"ns": 828, "exists": "", "*": "Module:Arguments"}], "images": ["The_Lord_of_the_Rings_Online_-_Saruman_receives_the_keys_to_Orthanc_from_Beren.jpg", "CdxIconArticleDisambiguation.svg"], "wikitext": {"*": "{{short description|19th Steward of Gondor}}\n{{disambig-more|Beren|[[Beren (disambiguation)]]}}\n{{infobox character\n| people=[[Gondorians|Gondorian]]\n| name=Beren\n| image=The Lord of the Rings Online - Saruman receives the keys to Orthanc from Beren.jpg\n| caption=''[[The Lord of the Rings Online]]'' tapestry: \"Saruman the White receives the keys to Orthanc from Beren, Steward of Gondor\"\n| pronun=\n| othernames=\n| titles=[[Ruling Steward]]\n| position=\n| location=[[Gondor]]\n| affiliation=\n| language=[[Westron]], [[Sindarin]]\n| birth={{TA|2655}}\n| birthlocation=\n| rule={{TA|2743}} - {{TA|2763|n}} (20 years)\n| death={{TA|2763}}\n| deathlocation=\n| age=108\n| notablefor=\n| house=[[House of Húrin]]\n| parentage=[[Egalmoth (Steward of Gondor)|Egalmoth]]\n| siblings=\n| spouse=\n| children=[[Beregond (Steward of Gondor)|Beregond]]\n| gender=Male\n| height=\n| hair=\n| eyes=\n| clothing=\n| weapons=\n| steed=\n}}\n'''Beren''' ([[Third Age]] 2655<ref>{{PM|Elendil}}, p. 205</ref> – 2763,<ref name=\"South\">{{App|South}}</ref> aged 108 years) was the nineteenth [[Ruling Steward]] of [[Gondor]].\n==History==\nBeren succeeded his father [[Egalmoth (Steward of Gondor)|Egalmoth]] at his death in {{TA|2743}}.<ref name=\"South\"/> \n\nBeren spent much of his rule fighting the [[Corsairs of Umbar]] for the [[Outlands|coasts]] were assailed by three great fleets from [[Umbar]] and from [[Harad]] up to the mouth of [[Isen]]. During the [[Long Winter]] of {{TA|2758}} - {{TA|2759|n}}, [[Rohan]] came under attack from the [[Dunlendings]], but as both nations were under attack neither could help each other. Before spring his son [[Beregond (Steward of Gondor)|Beregond]] overcame the invaders and was able to send help to Rohan and  fulfill the [[Oath of Eorl]].\n\nAfter the wars, [[Saruman]] suddenly appeared and requested leave to dwell in [[Isengard]], and Beren gladly gave the [[Wizard]] the [[key of Orthanc]].<ref>{{App|Stewards}}</ref>\n\nBeregond followed Beren at his death in {{TA|2763|n}}.<ref name=\"South\"/>\n\n==Genealogy==\n{{familytree/start}}\n{{familytree | | | BEL | | |BEL=[[Belecthor I]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2545|n}} - {{TA|2655|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |,|-|^|-|.| |}}\n{{familytree | ORO | | MOR |ORO=[[Orodreth (Steward of Gondor)|Orodreth]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2576|n}} - {{TA|2685|n}}''</small>|MOR=[[Morwen (daughter of Belecthor)|Morwen]]<br/><small>''unknown''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| | | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | ECT | | UNK |ECT=[[Ecthelion I]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2600|n}} - {{TA|2698|n}}''</small>|UNK=''Unknown''<br/><small>''unknown''</small>}}\n{{familytree | | | | | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | | | | | EGA |EGA=[[Egalmoth (Steward of Gondor)|Egalmoth]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2626|n}} - {{TA|2743|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | | | | | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | | | | | BER |BER='''BEREN'''<br/><small>''{{TA|2655|n}} - {{TA|2763|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | | | | | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | | | | | BER |BER=[[Beregond (Steward of Gondor)|Beregond]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2700|n}} - {{TA|2811|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | | | | | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | | | | | BEL |BEL=[[Belecthor II]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2752|n}} - {{TA|2872|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree/end}}\n\n==Portrayal in adaptations==\n'''2012: ''[[The Lord of the Rings Online]]'':'''\n: A tapestry depicting Saruman and Beren is found in [[Meduseld]].\n\n{{references}}\n{{seq-start}}\n{{seq-head\n| race=gondorian\n| house=[[House of Húrin]]\n| born={{TA|2655}}\n| died={{TA|2763}}\n}}\n{{seq\n| prev=[[Egalmoth (Steward of Gondor)|Egalmoth]]\n| list=19th [[Ruling Steward|Ruling Steward of Gondor]]\n| dates={{TA|2743}} - {{TA|2763|n}}\n| next=[[Beregond (Steward of Gondor)|Beregond]]\n}}\n{{seq-end}}\n{{rulingstewards}}\n{{title}}\n[[Category:Gondorians]]\n[[Category:House of Húrin]]\n[[Category:Ruling stewards]]\n[[Category:Third Age characters]]\n\n[[de:Beren (Truchsess von Gondor)]]\n[[fi:Beren (Gondorin käskynhaltija)]]\n[[fr:encyclo:personnages:hommes:3a:dunedain:gondoriens:beren]]"}}}